{"title": "How do I Search and Filter User Groups?", "body": "To filter and search for User Group, follow these steps:\nGo to More > Settings. \nClick User Group\nChoose User Group\nTo filter User Group: \nClick Filter, then you will be presented with the Status (1) Active and (2) Inactive. You can select both, to show Active and Inactive User Group, or choose one which User Group Status you would like to see.\nGroup Type will be in Default to Activity Group.\nTo search for a User Group:\nType in the Name of the User Group you are looking for in the Search Bar\nHit Enter or click the Magnifying glass icon to Search, and then you'll be presented with the Search results\nHow to Add a User to a User Group"}